WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.570 --> 00:00:04.730
High quality designs become more important as the size of the application being

00:00:04.730 --> 00:00:09.360
designed grows. But as the size grows, so too does the likelihood of some kind

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:14.090
of design flaw occur. It therefore becomes essential to validate the designs and

00:00:14.090 --> 00:00:18.490
the most common way of doing so is with design reviews. This lesson looks at

00:00:18.490 --> 00:00:23.600
design reviews, the participant's roles. The process of performing them and

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:26.520
general guidelines for producing effective reviews.

